title: Tree of Life Cafe & Bakery
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Take-out, Bakery, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Self-described as an urban cafeteria where slow food is served fast and its origin story is of renewal and restoration where tables are made of reclaimed barnwood and chairs re-purposed and refinished. Labels what's gluten-free, vegetarian, and vegan (check for honey). Est. Mar 2016.
